node.text: Ahlan wa Sahlan, my friend & #EidMubarak to you! 🌙 Heavily inspired by my big brother, @zayne81’s recent post and tapping into my Arabic heritage, I came up with this #genderneutral #Eid makeup look. I used colours from the #MACArtLibrary palette #NudeModel, #KohlPower pencil in #Feline & the #MACMosaicMasterpiece edition of In Extreme Dimension #3DBlack mascara. Shop this look on @lazada_sg MAC Flagship Store today! #MLYB #MACCosmetics #MACCosmeticsSG #MACAPACArtistry #MACArtist #MACMyDay #MACMeUpSG #TrendMACUp #Eid #StayHome #StayHomeSG #CircuitBreakerSG
@syabillopez “you’ll never have a (boy)friend like me” 🧞‍♂️*cue dance sequence
@junitakj hehehe it’s actually the opening song to Aladdin, “Arabian Nights” 🧞‍♂️
The music is EPIC!!!! Omar Shariff will approve!

Selamat Hari Raya to you abang!!😍
@schizoblurb Selamat Hari Raya Shariffah 🥰 thank you for supporting me & MAC all Ramadan!
